      Vitamin C and zinc are the two nutrients most studied together for immune support, and
      this combines both in one Rs. 23/day tablet. The pick for cold-and-flu season, frequent
      travellers, and anyone run down.
    </p>
  </ProductCard>

  <ProductCard rank={3} name={products[2].name} price={products[2].display} url={products[2].url} badge={products[2].badge}>
